<D>__{isn't it?}
<C>__{bernie}
<D>__{i like to think that's what's happened with you and me ... even though you're kinda my boss. still maybe it won't always be that way, huh?}
<A>__{david doesn't quite see what bernie is getting at but smiles politely. now we see bean's plan he has emerged at a nearby window. he can't reach the painting at first. so he stretches further and further out the window. no good. finally he has to go out on the ledge. he shoos away the birds, who then decide to settle on him instead. finally he gets a hand on the painting. as he does so, he loses hold. he just manages to grabs a window before he falls.}
<C>__{david}
