<D>__{thanks, david. always a pleasure.}
<A>__{period. bean is slowly managing to claw his way back towards the open window with the painting. it is an extraordinary piece of acrobatics. david turns to go.}
<C>__{bernie}
<D>__{by the way. don't know what you think, mr vice president, but i've been hinting to the old man that someone's got to have the balls to take some sort of emergency measures around here or we're all in the crap house. what do you think?}
